# Claude Workspace

Central file cabinet for Claude Code autonomous operations, subagent coordination, and multi-API integrations.

## Structure

```
claude-workspace/
├── .claude/                    # Subagent system (already configured)
│   ├── agents/                 # 17 specialized agents
│   ├── context/                # Session state management
│   ├── reports/                # Session-level reports
│   └── agent-registry.md       # Agent quick reference
│
├── projects/                   # Active project workspaces
│   └── {project-name}/         # Individual project folders
│
├── reports/                    # Historical reports
│   ├── daily/                  # Daily summaries
│   ├── weekly/                 # Weekly rollups
│   └── sprint/                 # Sprint retrospectives
│
├── knowledge/                  # Persistent knowledge base
│   ├── apis/                   # API documentation & credentials setup
│   ├── patterns/               # Reusable code patterns
│   ├── decisions/              # Architecture decision records (ADRs)
│   └── runbooks/               # Operational procedures
│
├── templates/                  # Reusable templates
│   ├── agents/                 # Agent definition templates
│   ├── workflows/              # n8n workflow templates
│   └── projects/               # Project scaffolding
│
├── integrations/               # External service configs
│   ├── n8n/                    # n8n workflow exports
│   ├── mcp/                    # MCP server configurations
│   └── webhooks/               # Webhook endpoint configs
│
└── data/                       # Data storage
    ├── exports/                # Exported data
    ├── imports/                # Data to process
    └── cache/                  # Temporary cached data
```

## Quick Start

### Initialize a New Project
```bash
cp -r templates/projects/default projects/my-new-project
cd projects/my-new-project
```

### Start a Session
```
Use the project-manager agent to initialize today's session
```

### Generate Reports
```
Use the project-manager agent to generate today's daily report
```

## GitHub Sync

This repository syncs to GitHub for:
- Version history of all changes
- Collaboration across machines
- Backup and disaster recovery
- GitHub Actions automation

## Integrations

### n8n Workflows
Workflow definitions stored in `integrations/n8n/`. Import into n8n for:
- Scheduled report generation
- API monitoring
- Data synchronization

### MCP Servers
Configuration in `integrations/mcp/`. Enables Claude to:
- Query databases directly
- Access external APIs
- Manage files across systems

## Maintenance

- **Daily**: Reports auto-generated in `reports/daily/`
- **Weekly**: Roll up daily reports every Sunday
- **Monthly**: Archive old reports, prune cache
